<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
<title>레미콘 지도 (2025)</title>

<!-- ✅ 로컬 vendor (CDN 차단 대비) -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet.markercluster@1.5.3/dist/MarkerCluster.css"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet.markercluster@1.5.3/dist/MarkerCluster.Default.css"/>

<script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet.markercluster@1.5.3/dist/leaflet.markercluster.js"></script>

<style>
  html, body, #map { height: 100%; margin: 0; }
  body { overflow: hidden; background:#fff; }
  #map { background: #fff; }

  .fatal {
    position: absolute; left: 12px; right: 12px; top: 12px;
    z-index: 10000;
    background: rgba(255,235,235,0.98);
    border: 1px solid #ff9a9a;
    color: #7a0000;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-family: -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,"Noto Sans KR","Apple SD Gothic Neo",sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
  }
  .fatal small { display:block; margin-top:6px; color:#7a0000; opacity:.85; }

  .panel, .panel2 {
    position: absolute; top: 10px; z-index: 9999;
    width: 360px;
    max-width: calc(100vw - 24px);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
    border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  .panel  { left: 10px; }
  .panel2 { right: 10px; width: 460px; }

  .panel input, .panel2 input {
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    font-size: 14px; outline: none;
  }

  .hint { margin-top: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }

  .results {
    margin-top: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    border-radius: 12px;
    max-height: 320px;
    overflow: auto;
    display: none;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .item {
    padding: 8px 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f2f2f2;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .item:hover { background: #f7fafc; }
  .sub { color:#667; font-size:11px; margin-top:2px; }
  .disabled { opacity:0.55; cursor: default; }
  .disabled:hover { background: transparent; }

  .topNote{ margin-top: 6px; font-size: 11px; color: #666; line-height: 1.35; }

  .btnRow{ display:flex; gap:8px; margin-top:8px; }
  .btn{
    flex:1;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    font-size: 13px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .btn:hover{ background:#f7fafc; }

  /* ✅ 우측 리스트: 상하폭/간격 줄이기 */
  .topWrap{
    margin-top: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: auto;
    background: #fff;
    max-height: calc(100vh - 190px);
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .topWrap::-webkit-scrollbar{ display:none; }

  table.topTable{
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 11px;
    table-layout: fixed;
  }
  table.topTable thead th{
    background:#fafafa;
    font-weight: 800;
    color:#222;
    padding: 6px 4px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    text-align: left;
  }
  table.topTable tbody td{
    padding: 5px 4px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  table.topTable th, table.topTable td{
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }
  table.topTable tbody tr:hover{ background:#f7fafc; }
  tr.hl { font-weight: 800; }
  tr.ajou, tr.ajou b { color:#c40000; }
  tr.ajou .sub { color:#c40000; opacity:.85; }

  /* 업체/공장 칼럼은 2줄 허용(간격 줄이기) */
  .nameCell {
    white-space: normal !important;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .nameCell .c { font-weight: 800; }
  .nameCell .f { color:#445; font-size: 10px; }

  .foot {
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #777;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .count{
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color:#667;
  }

  .wm{
    position: fixed;
    left: 14px;
    bottom: 10px;
    z-index: 900;
    font-family: "Pretendard Variable", Pretendard, "SUIT", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Noto Sans KR", system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.92);
    font-weight: 650;
    text-rendering: geometricPrecision;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    user-select: none;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }


  .pin-wrap{ background: transparent; border: none; }
  .pin-svg{ filter: drop-shadow(0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)); }

  /* ===== Mobile Optimizations (v7-mobile) ===== */
  #mobileBar { display:none; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    body { overflow: hidden; }
    #mobileBar{
      display:flex;
      gap:8px;
      position:absolute;
      left:12px;
      top:12px;
      z-index:10001;
    }
    .mBtn{
      border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-family: -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,"Noto Sans KR","Apple SD Gothic Neo",sans-serif;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }
    .panel, .panel2{
      left:12px !important;
      right:12px !important;
      width: auto !important;
      top: 60px !important; /* leave space for toggle buttons */
      max-height: calc(100vh - 86px);
    }
    .panel2 { top: 60px !important; }
    .panel.hiddenMobile, .panel2.hiddenMobile { display:none; }

    /* Larger tap targets */
    .panel input, .panel2 input { font-size: 16px; padding: 12px 12px; }
    .results .row { padding: 12px 10px; }
    .btn { padding: 12px 12px; font-size: 15px; }
  }

</style>
</head>

<body>
<div id="map"></div>

<div id="mobileBar" aria-label="모바일 패널 토글">
  <button class="mBtn" id="btnToggleLeft">업체검색</button>
  <button class="mBtn" id="btnToggleRight">거리계산</button>
</div>

<div class="fatal" id="fatal">
  지도를 초기화하는 중입니다…<br/>
  <small id="fatalSub">흰 화면이면: (1) 인터넷 연결/사내망 차단 여부 (2) 개발자도구(F12) Console 오류 확인</small>
</div>

<div class="panel">
  <input id="q" placeholder="업체/공장/주소 검색 (예: 아주, 수원, 용인...)"/>
  <div class="hint">Enter: 첫 결과로 이동 · 클릭: 해당 결과로 이동</div>
  <div class="count" id="resultCount"></div>
  <div class="results" id="results"></div>
</div>

<div class="panel2">
  <input id="site" placeholder="현장주소 입력 후 Enter (예: 서울 서초구 강남대로 351)"/>
  <div class="topNote">※ ‘현장주소’는 키 없이 OSM Nominatim으로 주소→좌표 변환(인터넷 필요)</div>
  <div class="btnRow">
    <button class="btn" id="btnCalc">거리 계산하기</button>
    <button class="btn" id="btnClear">현장표시 지우기</button>
  </div>
  <div id="top"></div>
  <div class="foot">※ 직선거리 기준</div>
</div>

<div class="wm" id="wm">아주산업(주)</div>

